tags.name:
wave-player
`A player for visualizing a sound file`
tags.jsDoc:
/**
 * `wave-player`
 * @customElement wave-player
 * `A player for visualizing a sound file`
 *

 * @polymer
 * @polymerLegacy
 * @demo demo/index.html
 */

attributes.name: src
attributes.description: The source of the audio file to be played
attributes.jsDoc:
/**
       * The source of the audio file to be played
       *
       * @attribute src
       * @type String
       * @default NULL
       */

attributes.name: title
attributes.description: The main (bold) title
attributes.jsDoc:
/**
       * The main (bold) title
       *
       * @attribute title
       * @type String
       * @default NULL
       */

attributes.name: subtitle
attributes.description: The smaller subtitle, for chapter heading or composer.
attributes.jsDoc:
/**
       * The smaller subtitle, for chapter heading or composer.
       *
       * @attribute subtitle
       * @type String
       * @default NULL
       */

attributes.name: coverart
attributes.description: The sourse for cover art
attributes.jsDoc:
/**
       * The sourse for cover art
       *
       * @attribute coverart
       * @type String
       * @default art.jpg
       */

attributes.name: wavesurfer
attributes.description: container for the wave object
attributes.jsDoc:
/**
       * container for the wave object
       *
       * @attribute wavesurfer
       * @type Object
       */

attributes.name: lean
attributes.description: Determines if the FOB is on the left or the right
attributes.jsDoc:
/**
       * Determines if the FOB is on the left or the right
       *
       * @attribute lean
       * @type String
       * @default left
       */

attributes.name: wavecolor
attributes.description: Color of the Wave
attributes.jsDoc:
/**
       * Color of the Wave
       *
       * @attribute wavecolor
       * @type String
       * @default #ffffff
       */

attributes.name: progresscolor
attributes.description: Color of the completed section of the wave
attributes.jsDoc:
/**
       * Color of the completed section of the wave
       *
       * @attribute progresscolor
       * @type String
       * @default #CFD8DC
       */
